    • GcpAsyncBlobStore

      public GcpAsyncBlobStore(AbstractBlobStore blobStore, ExecutorService executorService, com.google.cloud.storage.Storage storage, GcpTransformerSupplier transformerSupplier)
      Creates a new async wrapper around the provided BlobStore.
      Parameters:
      blobStore - the synchronous blob store to wrap
      executorService - the executor service to use for async operations. If this value is null then this will use the ForkJoinPool.commonPool()
      storage - the GCP Storage client for directory operations
      transformerSupplier - the transformer supplier for GCP operations
